{"tid":1513412,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大陸人+香港+謀殺=淨係坐6碌","createTime":"2019-08-28T10:15:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T10:53:04.000Z","uid":10014,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7c9a4b86a3d97ee61fd4d55083acf168ea9c1fea","tid":1513412,"uid":10014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T10:15:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/28/181526_06727ac68d14f92917e0680b236753fa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F28%2F181526_06727ac68d14f92917e0680b236753fa.png&h=db2cfa68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n從內地來港定居的21歲青年失業兩年賦閒在家，沉迷三級暴力血腥電玩，稱為此對血產生慾望，追求刺激興奮感，更好奇殺人有何感覺。去年他因不滿30歲中度智障友人經常「放飛機」不赴約，遂以對方為目標實行「殺人遊戲」，仿效他看過的電影情節打算把友人肢解。他先約友人上門「玩新嘢」，將對方蒙眼綁手後，以刀狂刺其頸，其後見滿地鮮血恐懼感湧現才報警。青年今於高等法院承認企圖謀罪，判監6年。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190828&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59982089\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190828%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59982089&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5Apem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=e55e20bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190828%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59982089&h=ef92f625\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190828&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59982089</a>"},{"pid":"dbc6dbeb896ae289c94fb40bb660198139ba1bc0","tid":1513412,"uid":10014,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T10:16:36.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一見到呢啲新聞我就好想香港獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong>"},{"pid":"096d43bb3db529d788bbd32fed91d39e18c0844d","tid":1513412,"uid":91604,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T10:21:59.000Z